      <h1>Local context &amp; searches</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Everything outside the property boundary that affects it — what the
        local authority records, what the Local Land Charges register lists,
        and what the environmental searches return. Three sub-pages by
        search type.
      </p>

      <aside class="callout callout--key" role="note">
        <p class="callout__label">The shape of this cluster</p>
        <p>
          Each search has its own authority, its own reply schema, and its
          own validity window. CON29R is the local-authority enquiries
          (planning, highways, contaminated land). LLC1 is the statutory
          charges register entry list. Environmental searches stitch in
          flood, mining, ground stability, and contaminated land risk.
          CON29DW (water and drainage) is a notable absence in this schema
          cut — there is no dedicated path for it yet; water-related leaves
          live on the Utilities &amp; energy page.
        </p>
      </aside>

      <h2 id="subpages">Pages in this cluster</h2>
      <ul class="cluster-index">
        <li><a href="46a-con29r.html"><strong>Local authority (CON29R)</strong></a> — local-authority identity and CON29R replies; listing &amp; conservation.</li>
        <li><a href="46c-llc1.html"><strong>Local Land Charges (LLC1)</strong></a> — LLC1 register entries; other one-off searches.</li>
        <li><a href="46d-environmental.html"><strong>Environmental</strong></a> — flood, mining, ground stability, contaminated land.</li>
      </ul>

      <PageFooter
  prev={{ href: '45-utilities-energy.html', label: 'Utilities & energy' }}
